558
00:36:39,119 --> 00:36:41,663
{\an8}Mereka yang tak tahu
Eunseom punya <i>benetbeot </i>akan tertipu.

559
00:36:41,746 --> 00:36:42,664
{\an8}BENETBEOT: KEMBAR

